#@host = http://92.38.48.35:5000
@host = https://lockium.kz

@deviceId = AY000001
@channel = 1
@boardNumber = 1
@irId = 1

### Get JWT access token by password and user login
# @name loginReq
POST {{host}}/api/v1/authenticate
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username":"admin",
    "password":"q1234567q"
}

### Connected devices
GET {{host}}/api/lock/devices
Authorization: Bearer {{loginReq.response.body.token}}

###

### Channel close
POST {{host}}/api/lock/{{deviceId}}/channels/{{channel}}/close?boardNumber={{boardNumber}}

###

### Keep channel open (relay/light — not for pulse locks)
POST {{host}}/api/lock/{{deviceId}}/channels/{{channel}}/keep-open?boardNumber={{boardNumber}}

###

### Open few channel locks (channels 1, 2, 3)
POST {{host}}/api/lock/{{deviceId}}/channels/open-few
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "channels": [1, 2, 3],
  "boardNumber": 0
}

###

### Open single channel lock (no order)
POST {{host}}/api/lock/{{deviceId}}/channels/{{channel}}/open
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginReq.response.body.token}}

{
  "boardNumber": "1"
}

### Open single channel lock (with order number)
POST {{host}}/api/lock/{{deviceId}}/channels/{{channel}}/open
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderNumber": "ORDER001",
  "boardNumber": 0
}

###

### Read IR (0x73): WKLY + len + board + 73 + irId + XOR
GET {{host}}/api/lock/{{deviceId}}/ir/{{irId}}?boardNumber=1
Authorization: Bearer {{loginReq.response.body.token}}

###

### Read single channel lock status
GET {{host}}/api/lock/{{deviceId}}/channels/{{channel}}/status?boardNumber={{boardNumber}}

###

### Read all channel lock status
GET {{host}}/api/lock/{{deviceId}}/status/all?boardNumber=1
Authorization: Bearer {{loginReq.response.body.token}}

###

### Posting the door status actively (all devices)
GET {{host}}/api/lock/door-status

###

### Posting the door status actively (filter by device)
GET {{host}}/api/lock/door-status?deviceId={{deviceId}}

###
